&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id="markdown-references"&gt;Markdown references
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Markdown (Simplified Chinese): &lt;a class="link" href="http://wowubuntu.com/markdown/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
